    "title": "Wanawake Wanaoitwa Maria",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "wanawake wanaoitwa maria",
    "language": "swh",
    "content": "<p>Injili zinawataja Maria wengine wanne kando na mama wa Yesu:</p><ol><li><p><em>Maria Magdalene, </em>ambaye huenda alitoka Magdala huko Galilaya, alikombolewa kutoka kwa pepo wachafu na Yesu (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark16:9\">Marko 16:9</a>). Alikuwa mfuasi mwaminifu na alisaidia Yesu na wanafunzi wake kifedha (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke8:1-Luke8:3\">Luka 8:1–3</a>; tazama pia <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt27:55-Matt27:56\">Mathayo 27:55–56</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark15:40-Mark15:41\">Marko 15:40–41</a>). Alishuhudia kifo cha Yesu msalabani na mazishi yake (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt27:55-Matt27:61\">Mathayo 27:55–61</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark15:40-Mark15:47\">Marko 15:40–47</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John19:25\">Yohana 19:25</a>; linganisha <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke23:49\">Luka 23:49</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke23:55-Luke23:56\">55–56</a>). Alienda kaburini mapema Jumapili asubuhi na manukato ya mazishi. Alikuwa miongoni mwa wa kwanza kusikia kwamba Yesu alikuwa amefufuka kutoka kwa wafu (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt28:1-Matt28:8\">Mathayo 28:1–8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark16:1-Mark16:8\">Marko 16:1–8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke24:1-Luke24:11\">Luka 24:1–11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke24:22-Luke24:24\">22–24</a>). Pia alikuwa wa kwanza kumwona Yesu aliyefufuka (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt28:9-Matt28:10\">Mathayo 28:9–10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark16:9-Mark16:11\">Marko 16:9–11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John20:1-John20:2\">Yohana 20:1–2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John20:11-John20:18\">11–18</a>).</p></li><li><p><em>Maria, mama wa Yakobo mdogo</em> (sio mtume) na Yosefu, alikuwa miongoni mwa wanawake waliokuwepo wakati wa kifo cha Yesu msalabani na mazishi yake (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt27:55-Matt27:61\">Mathayo 27:55–61</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark15:40-Mark15:47\">Marko 15:40–47</a>; tazama pia <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke23:49\">Luka 23:49</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke23:55\">55</a>). Kama Maria Magdalene, alikuwa miongoni mwa wa kwanza kusikia kwamba Yesu alikuwa amefufuka kutoka kwa wafu (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt28:1-Matt28:8\">Mathayo 28:1–8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark16:1-Mark16:8\">Marko 16:1–8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke24:1-Luke24:11\">Luka 24:1–11</a>). Alikuwa pia mmoja wa wa kwanza kumuona Yesu aliyefufuka (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt28:9-Matt28:10\">Mathayo 28:9–10</a>).</p></li><li><p><em>Maria wa Bethania</em> alikuwa dada wa Martha na Lazaro. Yesu aliipenda sana familia yao (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/John11:5\">Yohana 11:5</a>). Yesu alimsifu Maria kwa hamu yake ya kujifunza kutoka kwake (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke10:38-Luke10:42\">Luka 10:38–42</a>). Baada ya Yesu kumfufua kaka yake kutoka kwa wafu (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/John11:32-John11:45\">Yohana 11:32–45</a>), Maria alipaka miguu ya Yesu mafuta ya thamani kubwa. Yesu alimkinga alipokosolewa na wengine kwa kusema ilikuwa ni upotevu (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:1-John12:11\">Yohana 12:1–11</a>; linganisha <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:6-Matt26:13\">Mathayo 26:6–13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:3-Mark14:9\">Marko 14:3–9</a>).</p></li><li><p><em>Maria, mke wa Klopa,</em> alikuwa miongoni mwa wanawake waliokuwa wakimwangalia Yesu alipokufa msalabani (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/John19:25\">Yohana 19:25</a>). Agano Jipya halimtaji yeye wala Klopa sehemu nyingine yoyote.</p></li></ol><p><u>Sehemu za Kujifunza Zaidi</u></p><p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt27:55-Matt27:61\">Mathayo 27:55–61</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt28:1\">28:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark15:40-Mark15:47\">Marko 15:40–47</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark16:1-Mark16:11\">16:1–11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke8:2-Luke8:3\">Luka 8:2–3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke10:38-Luke10:42\">10:38–42</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke24:1-Luke24:10\">24:1–10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John11:1-John11:6\">Yohana 11:1–6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John11:17-John11:24\">17–24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:3-John12:8\">12:3–8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John19:25\">19:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John20:1-John20:2\">20:1–2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John20:11-John20:18\">11–18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts12:12\">Matendo 12:12</a></p>",
